{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bdd2d735f7","title":"帮助越南训练和装备新兵","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3203b3d885","index":0,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"bdd2d735f7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"7266d44b75","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"bdd2d735f7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东关于帮助越南训练和装备新兵问题为中共中央起草的给中南局和广西省委的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"67b667155f","type":"title","text":"帮助越南训练和装备新兵！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"bdd2d735f7"},{"id":"7266d44b75","type":"paragraph","text":"中南局，并广西省委","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"bdd2d735f7"},{"id":"d76e90bf33","type":"paragraph","text":"越南方面提议调一万新兵到中国训练并装备为一个炮兵师，另外调一个步兵团（大约有五千人）到中国训练及装备。接云南省委电告该省前已担任训练及装备越方二万余人，现感武器和粮食两项均不足，难于担负新任务，因此拟允许该炮兵师及步兵团于高平战役胜利结束越桂道路畅通之后，大约在十月上句或中句开至广西境内适当地点（距离越南故人较远有粮食条件又能隐蔽之西军区担负装备及训练的责任。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"bdd2d735f7"}],"page":{"id":"13b25ab7c8","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"bdd2d735f7","start":108,"end":108}}}},"__N_SSG":true}